        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl2_Label1"><p>Iperius Console is the software that allows to monitor all your backups made with Iperius Backup, along with the possibility to start and schedule them remotely in a few clicks. With Iperius Console, you can also view information about connected PCs and group them into Workgroups, also interfacing directly with other products of the Iperius [&hellip;]</p>
</span><a id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl2_HyperLink2" href="https://www.iperiusbackup.net/en/monitoring-your-backups-with-iperius-console-installation-and-configuration/" target="_blank">Read more »»</a> 
