        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl3_Label1"><p>Do you know that due to your ineffective and less optimized IT platform you stand the chance of losing all your customers in no time? A research conducted by UK internet compendium reveals that a whopping 38 percent of UK online shoppers instantly abandon apps/online platforms that take more than 10 seconds to load. In [&hellip;]</p>
