        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl6_Label1"><p>It’s no doubt that VMware is one of the leaders in server virtualization. VMware vSphere Hypervisor, or ESXi, is a type-1 hypervisor that enables virtual machine or guest OS to run over a bare metal system. Major companies choose ESXi due its simplicity, reliability, and robustness. With such quality, VMware tends to cost us with [&hellip;]</p>
