            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl7_Label1"><p>A common problem that one can encounter when installing Iperius Backup as a service and setting up a schedule for it is to encounter errors accessing network paths. These errors generally occur only when the backup is run in the automatic mode according to a schedule, while backups run manually complete successfully. The cause of [&hellip;]</p>
